author: Neil Munro, Neil Munro
title: Science Magazine Apologizes for Associating Chinese Virus with China
description: Nature, one of the world's leading journals of biological sciences, urged scientists in an editorial this week to embrace the technical name favored by China's government for the deadly disease that emerged from the Chinese city of Wuhan.
